 data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"An\n                        tonino\">[An-]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>tonino\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Pio\">P̣ị[o]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Felici\">[Fel(ici)]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Augusto\">[Aug(usto)]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Parthico\">Parṭ[h](ico)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">Max(imo)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Britanni\n                        co\">[Britanni-]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>co\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">[M]ax(imo)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Germanico\">Gẹrm(anico)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">Ṃ[ax(imo)]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>pont(ifici) max(imo) trib(unicia) \u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">p͡o͡t\u003C/span>est(ate) [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>f(elicissimo?) p(io?) p(rincipi?) imp(eratori) \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">IIII\u003C/span> co(n)s(uli) \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">III\u003C/span>[I p(atri) p(atriae)] \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[proco(n)s(uli)] res [p(ublica)] \u003Cbr id=\"al8-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>[Lilybita]ṇo[rum] \u003Cbr id=\"al9-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, Alfredo Tosques\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Imperatori Caesari Marco Aurelio An\n                        tonino Pio Felici Augusto\n                    Parthico Maximo Britanni\n                        co Maximo\n                    Germanico Maximo\">..[.\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caesari\">.....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marco\">..\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aurelio\">....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"An\n                        tonino\">..]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>TONINO\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Pio\">..[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Felici\">....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Augusto\">....]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Parthico\">PAR.[.]\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">MAX\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Britanni\n                        co\">[........]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>CO\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">[.]AX\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Germanico\">G.RM\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">.[..]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>PONTMAXTRIB\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">P͡O͡T\u003C/span>EST[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>FPPIMP\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">IIII\u003C/span>COS\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">III\u003C/span>[.....]\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[.......]RES[..]\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>[........].O[...]\u003Cbr id=\"al9-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004406_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic004406_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004406.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic004406-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Silvestrini 2022\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text is notable for the presence at the start of line 6 of the letters F P P separated by interpuncts, and somewhat smaller than the other letters of the inscription, which seem to abbreviate a series of sigla/epithets honouring Caracalla, and which by comparison with various other honorifics for Caracalla Silvestrini proposes to read (speculatively) as felicissimus, pius, princeps.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Silvestrini 2020 298-299 no.2 with fig.6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002609\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002609\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Silvestrini 2022 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001579\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001579\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Tall narrow letters, with interpuncts and a combining ligature/monogram of POT in line 5.\u003C/p> Lines 1-8  55-65  Interlineation    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[209,212,215,218,221,224,227,230],{"id":210,"html":211},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, Alfredo Tosques\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Imperatori Caesari Marco Aurelio An\n                        tonino Pio Felici Augusto\n                    Parthico Maximo Britanni\n       