r\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Parthico\">PAR.[.]\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">MAX\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Britanni\n                        co\">[........]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>CO\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">[.]AX\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Germanico\">G.RM\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Maximo\">.[..]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>PONTMAXTRIB\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">P͡O͡T\u003C/span>EST[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>FPPIMP\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">IIII\u003C/span>COS\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">III\u003C/span>[.....]\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[.......]RES[..]\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>[........].O[...]\u003Cbr id=\"al9-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":213,"html":214},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004406_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic004406_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004406.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic004406-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":216,"html":217},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Silvestrini 2022\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":219,"html":220},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":222,"html":223},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text is notable for the presence at the start of line 6 of the letters F P P separated by interpuncts, and somewhat smaller than the other letters of the inscription, which seem to abbreviate a series of sigla/epithets honouring Caracalla, and which by comparison with various other honorifics for Caracalla Silvestrini proposes to read (speculatively) as felicissimus, pius, princeps.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":225,"html":226},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Silvestrini 2020 298-299 no.2 with fig.6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002609\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002609\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Silvestrini 2022 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001579\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001579\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":228,"html":229},"handnote","\u003Cp>Tall narrow letters, with interpuncts and a combining ligature/monogram of POT in line 5.\u003C/p> Lines 1-8  55-65  Interlineation    ",{"id":231,"html":232},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[234,236,239,240],{"html":235},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, Alfredo Tosques",{"id":237,"lang":128,"html":238},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1